question: Show me the model and operator of the camera that was last purchased.
sql_query1: SELECT Brand_Name, Cinematographer FROM Camera ORDER BY Purchase_Year DESC LIMIT 1
sql_query2: SELECT Camera_Type, Cinematographer FROM Camera ORDER BY Purchase_Year DESC LIMIT 1
sql_query3: SELECT Brand_Name, Camera_Type, Cinematographer FROM Camera ORDER BY Purchase_Year DESC LIMIT 1
interpretation1: Show me the brand name and operator of the camera that was last purchased?
interpretation2: Show me the camera type and operator of the camera that was last purchased?
interpretation3: Show me the brand name, camera type and operator of the camera that was last purchased?
sql_query_general: SELECT Camera_Model, Cinematographer FROM Camera ORDER BY Purchase_Year DESC LIMIT 1
